text:
Great Muslim food store serving popular dishes like Ayam and Fish Penyet, Oxtail Soup, and economy rice options. Gets busy during lunch.
Efficient and friendly service by the owners giving you an extra smile to your day.
You got to go there, eat their food and then see why I rated them 5 stars. Awesome, delicious food and service... Atmosphere so bright and spacious. Loved everything.
